  "text": "Sixty-seven peach accessions were used in this experiment (Table 1 ). The genomic DNA was extracted from young leaves by the optimized CTAB method as previously described [CITATION_1] , and the concentration was measured spectrophotometrically at 260 nm. The purified DNA was adjusted to a working solution of 40 ng/μL.",
